          <p class="mh-founder-p">MedhaIQ is built on more than 25 years of leading global consulting engagements, digital transformation programs, and enterprise talent initiatives across North America, EMEA, and APAC. Decades across multinational ecosystems reveal a consistent truth: technical expertise alone rarely determines career progression. The professionals who create the greatest impact combine deep domain knowledge with exceptional communication, executive presence, and strategic judgment.</p>
          <p class="mh-founder-p">As organizations increasingly assess leadership potential, business acumen, and communication alongside technical capability, many professionals struggle to demonstrate executive readiness when it matters most.</p>

          <h3 class="mh-founder-sub-title">The MedhaIQ Architecture</h3>
          <p class="mh-founder-p">MedhaIQ combines multiple leading AI models with enterprise-grade evaluation frameworks to deliver coaching aligned with the communication, decision-making, and leadership expectations of global organizations. Rather than simply simulating interview conversations, the platform provides structured, data-driven feedback that helps professionals strengthen executive communication, strategic thinking, and cross-functional stakeholder engagement over time.</p>

          <h3 class="mh-founder-sub-title">The Vision</h3>
          <p class="mh-founder-p">Our ambition extends well beyond interview preparation. We are building the AI-powered Career Operating System that enables professionals to continuously assess, develop, and demonstrate leadership capabilities throughout their careers—not just before an interview.</p>

